subSubSection.paragraph:
Remarks. This species is similar to
Tegonotus eupators
Huang, 2001
, but can be differentiated by prodorsal shield with small pits (prodorsal shield smooth in
T . eupators
); coxal area with short lines (coxal area smooth
T . eupators
); ventral annuli with elliptical microtubercles (ventral annuli with spiny microtubercles in
T . eupators
).
